       DETAIL
*      RJUST   RIGHT JUSTIFIES A BCD WORD 
*      INSERTS LEADING BLANKS. KEEPS LEADING ZEROS    
       LBL     RJUST
       ENTRY   RJUST    
RJUST  SYN     *  
X4     SYN     *-2
       SXD     X4,4     
       CAL*    1,4
       STI     A  
       AXT     6,4
B      PAI  
       IIR     60 
       RFT     77            SKIP WHEN BLANK ON RIGHT 
       TRA     C  
       ARS     6  
       ORA     =H 00000      INSERT LEADING BLANK     
       TIX     B,4,1    
       CAL     =H     *      ALL BLANK. SET *   
C      XCL  
       XCA  
       LDI     A  
       LXD     X4,4     
       TRA     2,4
A      PZE  
       END  
